8 Fall Decor Ideas for Your Porch

Decorate Your Door With Fall Wreaths and Garland


A fall wreath is a classic decoration that adds a welcoming touch to your front door and gives it an instant update. Paired alongside potted mums and freshly picked pumpkins, a wreath will help you create an outdoor dcor look youll love.


At Lowes, fall door wreaths come in many sizes and styles, allowing you to find one that suits your home. Check out floral wreaths or leaf wreaths, both crafted from lasting faux flowers or leaves that showcase the seasons hues of red, orange and gold. Other fall or autumn wreaths we carry incorporate more seasonal elements such as pumpkins and berries into the display. When shopping for a wreath, choose a style that complements your other outdoor fall decorations. Use small wreaths as centerpiece dcor on tables and medium wreaths for the doors and windows of your home. If you have high ceilings, doorways and large windows, you can invest in some large or oversized wreaths that will really make a statement.


Consider ways to display fall garland around your home. Find pumpkin and gourd garland that coordinates with your wreath and hang it over your front door. Decorate mantels or console tables with garland featuring leaves, faux flowers or pine cones to bring fall dcor indoors. You can also hang garland from outdoor fencing or around porch railings for an extra festive touch. As you prepare for fall, check out our guide 7 Fall Front Porch Ideas for instant inspiration.
